{"tid":674980,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：觀塘孔夫子","createTime":"2018-05-23T07:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T14:15:43.000Z","uid":181719,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"acd1800b24e32f022e0e1e0bc05437d60d009a25","tid":674980,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"有次去觀塘見到呢間野，諗住樓上舖應該唔爆，點知閒日walk in 竟然食唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  於是專登卜檯去食。要讚下佢啲位算幾闊落，唔會好似變相搭檯咁，坐得幾舒服。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/150245_b5435f195530948d9fd2aa7cf72badaf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F150245_b5435f195530948d9fd2aa7cf72badaf.jpeg&h=deeb0fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冷盤係酥皮茄子，睇落好工整，似一舊大蘑菇多過茄子，當然食落真係茄子黎嘅。炸皮做得薄脆，冇油益味，茄子亦冇乜索油。味道唔算特別出色，但係幾啱冷盤攞黎開胃而唔應該食滯嘅原意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/150311_ae910d9a485389162719af7510b1e033.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F150311_ae910d9a485389162719af7510b1e033.jpeg&h=a69ee00d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主菜叫咗個檸檬汁炸蝦球，放一塊檸檬喺底一條盧筍喺面，幾好睇，不過唔理解佢扮緊乜，食落味道相當出色，檸檬汁雖然做得偏甜，酸味唔夠，但配大件炸蝦球仍然相當好味，蝦肉又夠爽脆，我連續食咗3舊都完全冇膩感。食到第4舊開始有少少嘅，咪咬塊檸檬消吓滯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/150333_26c1b1bd69cd3b3fdb9e0d4b101e8164.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F150333_26c1b1bd69cd3b3fdb9e0d4b101e8164.jpeg&h=8f06b013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主食係銅盤沙薑雞飯，飯焗出黎嘅火候幾好，係老野講果種「蝦仔米」黎，通常呢種做法嘅飯，大家梗係會爭住食餸下面塾底果啲飯嘅，比我爭到（小小啦），但係只有沙薑味而冇雞味。當然啦，因為沙薑味本身太搶，飯冇雞味係非戰之罪。雞本身都嫩滑，有少少雞味啦，去骨上我自己唔太好，不過都係好味嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/150352_4ebeddf702d1674acd53d094e7d2ea6c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F150352_4ebeddf702d1674acd53d094e7d2ea6c.jpeg&h=4ae36be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n埋單4舊水咁上下，整體黎講我會揀呢間好過去同價位嘅酒樓。"},{"pid":"e7294453f3b662c16a128db8442a1f8553451443","tid":674980,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1f3c833c0014d800e116dc7e37276186860e95","tid":674980,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e7294453f3b662c16a128db8442a1f8553451443","tid":674980,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fde9d1c9f4446e1f74840bcb9d503e168b8f91","tid":674980,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:36:19.000Z","msg":"講漏咗，其實佢有10樣8樣招牌菜，但我一樣都冇叫到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38435c4ae66524981c496a855c8509d0b9e0d2c2","tid":674980,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:01:58.000Z","msg":"幾多人食"},{"pid":"e79f54ba644b394c3b9d97eb12224fd587a3c6d4","tid":674980,"uid":170979,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:04:19.000Z","msg":"三樣野成四舊水？"},{"pid":"2ca2184fbfda8e4c83346c7d145725a649d91876","tid":674980,"uid":6211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:08:51.000Z","msg":"食過, 好撚普通<br />\n得個片皮鴨好食D, 但唔熱既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n服務仲要好差<br />\n呢個價大把選擇唔使食佢"},{"pid":"5b3bcd497c671af2adb6392f8b46ea52fa0944fb","tid":674980,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"38435c4ae66524981c496a855c8509d0b9e0d2c2","tid":674980,"uid":956